<h2 class="bold font-l">Dr. Stone - The Stone Beam</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
One day, a mysterious green light covers the entire world, turning all humans into stone. After a short period of absolute terror, almost everyone falls into unconsciousness after losing their focus. Our heroes Senku and Taiju are apparently the only people who managed to remain focused and conscious, which will eventually allow them to break free from the petrification 3700 years later. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/TakenForGranite" class='trope-example-link'>Taken for Granite</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Dr Stone</span> </h3>
</div>
